DALAM DRAMA INI ADALAH FIKTIF

5
00:00:21,086 --> 00:00:22,087
Saeroyi.

6
00:00:39,187 --> 00:00:40,188
Aku...

7
00:00:42,524 --> 00:00:44,067
sudah berlutut di hadapanmu.

8
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:01,293
Kenapa kau begini?

9
00:01:02,460 --> 00:01:05,130
Ke mana prinsip hidup
yang kau pertahankan itu?

10
00:01:10,010 --> 00:01:11,970
Ini cukup untuk membuatmu berlutut?

11
00:01:16,725 --> 00:01:19,269
Pada akhirnya, kau menyerah
karena aku lebih berkuasa.

12
00:01:26,109 --> 00:01:27,611
Di mana Jang Geun-won?

13
00:01:35,911 --> 00:01:38,496
Padahal aku berharap
kau bisa menjadi hiburan terakhirku.

14
00:01:42,876 --> 00:01:44,544
Ternyata kau membosankan.

15
00:01:47,339 --> 00:01:49,758
Kau tak ada bedanya 
dengan pengemis.

16
00:01:54,095 --> 00:01:56,431
Tapi karena kau berlutut,

17
00:01:59,434 --> 00:02:02,103
aku harus membuang putraku kembali.

18
00:02:39,307 --> 00:02:41,685
Musuhku ini akhirnya berlutut juga.

19
00:02:43,228 --> 00:02:44,104
Sekarang...

20
00:02:45,814 --> 00:02:47,107
bagaimana perasaanmu?

21
00:02:53,780 --> 00:02:54,948
Aku merasa menyedihkan.

22
00:02:56,825 --> 00:02:57,826
Benarkah?

23
00:03:01,162 --> 00:03:03,957
- Pergi.
- Bagaimana perasaanmu, Pak?

24
00:03:10,296 --> 00:03:11,881
Dengan melihatku berlutut,

25
00:03:12,924 --> 00:03:14,092
apa kau senang?

26
00:03:24,310 --> 00:03:25,687
Apa kau puas?

27
00:03:27,897 --> 00:03:29,649
- Sekarang...
- Sampai sekarang,

28
00:03:30,734 --> 00:03:33,570
aku hidup membawa dendamku padamu.

29
00:03:38,867 --> 00:03:40,744
Presdir Jangga, Jang Dae-hee.

30
00:03:41,870 --> 00:03:42,954
Musuhku.

31
00:03:44,581 --> 00:03:47,500
Pria yang merusak hidupku,
tapi dia juga...

32
00:03:49,210 --> 00:03:50,503
pria yang hebat.

33
00:03:54,758 --> 00:03:57,469
Walau nilai kita berbeda,
aku mengakui kehebatanmu.

34
00:03:59,429 --> 00:04:00,472
Aku...

35
00:04:03,433 --> 00:04:05,310
mengikuti jejakmu

36
00:04:06,394 --> 00:04:07,812
seumur hidupku.

37
00:04:12,567 --> 00:04:13,568
Kupikir

38
00:04:15,862 --> 00:04:18,114
pertarungan ini memang pantas.

39
00:04:19,741 --> 00:04:21,659
- Tunggu.
- Tapi pria itu...

40
00:04:23,620 --> 00:04:24,662
mengancamku...

41
00:04:25,914 --> 00:04:28,291
untuk berlutut
dengan menculik orang terdekatku.

42
00:04:32,629 --> 00:04:35,715
Aku membuang beberapa belas tahun
untuk mengikuti jejak

43
00:04:35,799 --> 00:04:37,133
pria tua menjijikkan ini?

44
00:04:40,804 --> 00:04:42,555
Aku menyesal

45
00:04:46,684 --> 00:04:47,685
menyia-nyiakan hidupku.

46
00:04:51,564 --> 00:04:52,649
Lihat hasilnya.

47
00:04:53,942 --> 00:04:55,401
Kau berlutut di depanku, 'kan?

48
00:04:56,444 --> 00:04:57,904
Kadang untuk keuntungan...

49
00:05:01,449 --> 00:05:02,575
Ayo pergi, Seung-kwon.

50
00:05:03,243 --> 00:05:04,285
Baik.

51
00:05:27,767 --> 00:05:29,686
Setelah beberapa belas tahun,

52
00:05:31,062 --> 00:05:32,105
aku baru mengenalmu.

53
00:05:50,999 --> 00:05:53,543
EPISODE TERAKHIR

54
00:05:53,710 --> 00:05:54,752
Benar.

55
00:05:55,628 --> 00:05:57,338
Park Saeroyi atau siapalah itu.

56
00:05:58,214 --> 00:06:00,633
Ayo kita bunuh Jo Yi-seo dahulu.

57
00:06:21,404 --> 00:06:24,032
Tak usah buang tenaga. Kalian diam saja.

58
00:06:27,660 --> 00:06:28,745
Angkat itu.

59
00:06:39,380 --> 00:06:41,049
Astaga, aku takut sekali.

60
00:06:41,132 --> 00:06:42,091
Kenapa?

61
00:06:42,800 --> 00:06:45,136
Kau pikir kami takut dengan itu?

62
00:06:46,971 --> 00:06:48,181
Kalian konyol.

63
00:06:48,848 --> 00:06:51,643
Serang mereka pada hitungan ketiga.

64
00:06:54,312 --> 00:06:55,146
Ayo ke sini.

65
00:06:55,230 --> 00:06:56,356
Satu.

66
00:06:56,856 --> 00:06:58,691
Dua. Tiga.

67
00:06:58,775 --> 00:07:01,986
Jang Geun-soo, semangat! Bertahanlah!

68
00:07:10,662 --> 00:07:11,996
Tangkap gadis itu.

69
00:07:13,122 --> 00:07:14,457
Sialan.

70
00:07:14,540 --> 00:07:15,875
Jangan berani mendekat!

71
00:07:21,172 --> 00:07:22,465
Apa yang kau lakukan?

72
00:07:24,133 --> 00:07:25,093
Dia menyuruhku...

73
00:07:27,011 --> 00:07:27,971
untuk bertahan.

74
00:07:43,820 --> 00:07:46,030
Kau tahu, 'kan? Ini hal berbahaya.

75
00:07:49,784 --> 00:07:50,743
Aku...

76
00:07:52,370 --> 00:07:53,621
akan menyelamatkan Yi-seo.

77
00:07:55,456 --> 00:07:57,166
Aku tahu, karena itu kita ke sana.

78
00:07:59,585 --> 00:08:01,212
Kau harus pilih prioritasmu.

79
00:08:02,755 --> 00:08:03,589
Apa?

80
00:08:03,673 --> 00:08:05,675
Semua akan berantakan

81
00:08:05,800 --> 00:08:08,052
bila kau ragu ambil keputusan.

82
00:08:08,970 --> 00:08:10,138
Sekalipun

83
00:08:11,222 --> 00:08:13,683
aku dan kau bisa terluka,

84
00:08:14,976 --> 00:08:17,645
juga mati, Yi-seo tetap harus selamat.

85
00:08:20,231 --> 00:08:21,649
Begitu rupanya.

86
00:08:22,900 --> 00:08:26,112
Namun, aku tak bisa memaksamu
untuk tetap ikut denganku.

87
00:08:28,197 --> 00:08:30,908
Dasar aneh.
Kalau begitu, kenapa kau ajak aku?

88
00:08:34,454 --> 00:08:35,413
Yi-seo.

89
00:08:36,372 --> 00:08:38,124
Walau terkadang kurang ajar,

90
00:08:39,125 --> 00:08:40,835
kini dia keluarga.

91
00:08:42,170 --> 00:08:43,504
Dia juga penting bagiku.

92
00:08:44,005 --> 00:08:45,840
Tujuan kita harus sama...

93
00:08:47,175 --> 00:08:48,426
agar bisa bekerja sama dengan baik.

94
00:08:51,971 --> 00:08:53,014
Terima kasih.

95
00:08:53,723 --> 00:08:54,599
Tak masalah.

96
00:08:56,100 --> 00:08:58,686
Walau kau mati,
aku akan tetap selamatkan Yi-seo.

97
00:09:21,584 --> 00:09:22,418
Kau tak apa-apa?

98
00:09:23,961 --> 00:09:25,588
Ini kali pertamamu ditusuk, 'kan?

99
00:09:26,881 --> 00:09:30,968
Sia-sia berlagak keren
seperti yang kau lihat di film.

100
00:09:31,511 --> 00:09:32,762
Inilah realitanya.

101
00:09:42,355 --> 00:09:44,148
Kau ternyata pria sejati.

102
00:09:45,108 --> 00:09:46,109
Diam di tempat.

103
00:09:53,658 --> 00:09:54,742
Cukup.

104
00:09:57,286 --> 00:09:58,496
Kau tak tangkap Jo Yi-seo?

105
00:09:59,455 --> 00:10:00,289
Kau bisa kehilangan dia.

106
00:10:04,752 --> 00:10:05,628
Benar juga.

107
00:10:08,214 --> 00:10:09,298
Ayo berangkat.

108
00:10:22,520 --> 00:10:25,356
Kau sudah dapat semua yang kau inginkan,
termasuk Jangga, 'kan?

109
00:10:26,065 --> 00:10:27,859
Jangan ikut campur.

110
00:10:32,488 --> 00:10:33,823
Yang kuinginkan?

111
00:10:38,870 --> 00:10:40,955
Aku tak pernah dapatkan
hal itu seumur hidupku.

112
00:10:42,999 --> 00:10:44,125
Tak pernah sama sekali.

113
00:10:51,132 --> 00:10:52,175
Namun,

114
00:10:54,635 --> 00:10:56,929
kau dan aku ternyata memang saudara.

115
00:11:00,850 --> 00:11:02,018
Apa maksudmu?

116
00:11:03,978 --> 00:11:05,062
Kita selalu gunakan...

117
00:11:07,315 --> 00:11:08,608
cara yang salah.

118
00:11:13,946 --> 00:11:16,032
Dia sedang apa? Kau tak mau ikut?

119
00:11:19,577 --> 00:11:20,703
Pegang dia.

120
00:11:56,614 --> 00:11:57,740
Hei, Anak Kecil!

121
00:11:58,449 --> 00:11:59,825
Menyerah sajalah!

122
00:12:00,117 --> 00:12:01,827
Kau tak akan bisa lari dari kami!

123
00:12:02,745 --> 00:12:05,122
Kau saja yang menyerah, dasar preman!

124
00:12:09,126 --> 00:12:10,878
- Tangkap dia.
- Baik.

125
00:12:18,386 --> 00:12:19,512
Astaga.

126
00:12:20,596 --> 00:12:21,931
Dia benar-benar keras kepala.

127
00:12:53,671 --> 00:12:54,588
Sial.

128
00:13:13,065 --> 00:13:14,150
Tabrak dia.

129
00:13:50,019 --> 00:13:52,188
Kantong udaranya berfungsi sempurna.

130
00:13:52,271 --> 00:13:53,689
Untunglah.

131
00:13:56,692 --> 00:13:57,735
Sialan.

132
00:13:58,319 --> 00:13:59,820
Apa ini?

133
00:14:00,946 --> 00:14:01,864
Sial.

134
00:14:06,118 --> 00:14:07,119
Bos?

135
00:14:09,997 --> 00:14:11,040
Yi-seo.

136
00:14:15,127 --> 00:14:16,170
Bos...

137
00:14:17,463 --> 00:14:18,464
Bos!

138
00:14:34,730 --> 00:14:35,564
Kau tak apa-apa?

139
00:14:38,109 --> 00:14:39,318
Aku dengar kau terluka.

140
00:14:41,070 --> 00:14:44,699
Untuk apa kau ke sini? Apa kau gila?

141
00:14:46,367 --> 00:14:47,743
Park Saeroyi!

142
00:14:55,376 --> 00:14:56,627
Kau membantuku.

143
00:14:58,003 --> 00:15:00,631
Kau datang sendiri untuk mati, 'kan?

144
00:15:02,842 --> 00:15:03,843
Saeroyi.

145
00:15:06,429 --> 00:15:07,471
Hee-hoon.

146
00:15:08,848 --> 00:15:10,474
Untuk apa kau datang ke sini?

147
00:15:12,601 --> 00:15:14,895
Aku datang setelah lapor polisi.

148
00:15:17,982 --> 00:15:19,650
Apa kau tak bisa pergi saja?

149
00:15:20,317 --> 00:15:22,236
Dasar pengecut.

150
00:15:22,319 --> 00:15:23,487
Aduh, sakit.

151
00:15:26,449 --> 00:15:27,491
Sialan.

152
00:15:28,784 --> 00:15:30,995
Seung-kwon, kau baik-baik saja?

153
00:15:32,663 --> 00:15:35,458
Astaga, Direktur Jo. Senang mendengarmu
memanggilku begitu.

154
00:15:36,667 --> 00:15:37,668
Seung-kwon.

155
00:15:37,752 --> 00:15:40,129
Ya, aku tahu prioritasku.

156
00:15:43,966 --> 00:15:47,011
Cepat pergi. Aku akan urus ini.

157
00:15:51,766 --> 00:15:52,641
Ayo pergi.

158
00:15:57,146 --> 00:15:58,189
Sial.

159
00:16:02,359 --> 00:16:03,402
Choi Seung-kwon.

160
00:16:14,413 --> 00:16:15,331
Hajar dia.

161
00:16:22,797 --> 00:16:26,467
Astaga, dahulu kau teman kami.

162
00:16:26,967 --> 00:16:28,052
Kau tak kenal ampun.

163
00:16:29,261 --> 00:16:30,679
"Jangan ragu."

164
00:16:31,388 --> 00:16:33,307
Bukankah itu yang sering kau katakan?

165
00:16:35,226 --> 00:16:36,477
Sudah kuduga,

166
00:16:37,520 --> 00:16:39,647
- kau lebih cocok dengan kami.
- Tidak.

167
00:16:42,650 --> 00:16:44,443
Aku juga mahir melayani tamu.

168
00:17:16,976 --> 00:17:18,185
- Kau baik-baik saja?
- Ya.

169
00:17:19,103 --> 00:17:20,604
Untuk apa kau ke sini?

170
00:17:21,146 --> 00:17:22,189
Ayo.

171
00:17:26,944 --> 00:17:28,404
Aku teringat saat itu.

172
00:17:29,321 --> 00:17:30,781
Ketika kita berlari di Itaewon.

173
00:17:32,241 --> 00:17:34,201
Untuk apa kau tiba-tiba membicarakan itu?

174
00:17:36,078 --> 00:17:37,913
Karena aku sangat merindukanmu.

175
00:17:50,050 --> 00:17:51,135
Kau selalu...

176
00:17:53,053 --> 00:17:54,680
berusaha keras untukku selama ini.

177
00:17:56,640 --> 00:17:58,058
Kau selalu terluka.

178
00:18:02,021 --> 00:18:03,147
Apa ini?

179
00:18:05,232 --> 00:18:06,901
Kau sungguh baik-baik saja?

180
00:18:11,947 --> 00:18:12,865
Kenapa bisa begini?

181
00:18:21,415 --> 00:18:22,666
Pikiran...

182
00:18:25,961 --> 00:18:27,087
dan hatiku

183
00:18:35,095 --> 00:18:36,221
dipenuhi olehmu.

184
00:18:44,688 --> 00:18:46,273
Mungkin ini juga yang kau rasakan.

185
00:18:47,024 --> 00:18:47,983
Ternyata...

186
00:18:48,901 --> 00:18:50,069
ini membuatku gugup.

187
00:18:52,988 --> 00:18:53,822
Bos.

188
00:18:53,906 --> 00:18:54,949
Aku mencintaimu.

189
00:19:01,455 --> 00:19:02,623
Aku mencintaimu, Yi-seo.

190
00:19:09,838 --> 00:19:11,131
Aku sangat mencintaimu.

191
00:19:34,071 --> 00:19:35,698
Dasar gila.

192
00:20:01,056 --> 00:20:02,349
Pergi! Lari!

193
00:20:02,433 --> 00:20:04,560
Bagaimana aku bisa meninggalkanmu?

194
00:20:04,643 --> 00:20:06,353
Apa kau sengaja mau mati sendiri?

195
00:20:08,939 --> 00:20:10,607
Polisi akan meneleponmu.

196
00:20:10,691 --> 00:20:13,027
Angkat dan beri tahu posisi kita.

197
00:20:18,615 --> 00:20:21,118
Kalian berdua bersenang-senang, 'kan?

198
00:20:23,287 --> 00:20:24,997
Percaya padaku dan pergilah.

199
00:20:27,249 --> 00:20:28,459
Yi-seo.

200
00:20:31,378 --> 00:20:33,047
Dasar konyol.

201
00:20:34,006 --> 00:20:35,215
Bila kau mati,

202
00:20:36,300 --> 00:20:37,384
aku juga akan mati.

203
00:20:38,385 --> 00:20:39,970
Cepat pergi. Cepat!

204
00:20:41,680 --> 00:20:43,057
Hei!

205
00:20:53,358 --> 00:20:54,443
Sialan.

206
00:20:59,531 --> 00:21:01,366
Kau mau mati, 'kan?

207
00:21:01,658 --> 00:21:04,703
Aku dan Seung-kwon datang
untuk mempertaruhkan nyawa.

208
00:21:05,913 --> 00:21:09,333
Nyawamu sama sekali tak berharga bagiku.

209
00:21:11,168 --> 00:21:12,127
Dasar gila.

210
00:21:18,967 --> 00:21:19,843
Bos!

211
00:21:20,094 --> 00:21:21,178
Dasar berengsek!

212
00:21:25,849 --> 00:21:27,017
Lihat apa kau?

213
00:21:44,201 --> 00:21:45,244
<i>Hari ini,</i>

214
00:21:48,455 --> 00:21:49,498
<i>semua akan berakhir.</i>

215
00:22:00,551 --> 00:22:01,635
Berengsek!

216
00:22:06,390 --> 00:22:07,850
Mati saja kau!

217
00:22:08,350 --> 00:22:11,311
Seperti ayahmu!

218
00:22:17,401 --> 00:22:20,028
Bagaimana bisa kau masih mengaku manusia?

219
00:22:34,459 --> 00:22:38,338
Yi-seo, Geun-soo, Ho-jin,

220
00:22:39,089 --> 00:22:40,299
juga ayahku.

221
00:22:43,385 --> 00:22:45,470
Apa kau tak merasa bersalah sama sekali?

222
00:22:48,515 --> 00:22:50,392
Ketika makan daging babi,

223
00:22:50,976 --> 00:22:52,436
apa kau merasa bersalah?

224
00:22:53,353 --> 00:22:54,271
Apa?

225
00:22:54,354 --> 00:22:56,565
Karena babi-babi itu,

226
00:22:58,191 --> 00:22:59,276
semuanya lenyap.

227
00:23:00,193 --> 00:23:01,236
"Bersalah"?

228
00:23:02,029 --> 00:23:03,196
Omong kosong apa itu.

229
00:23:03,280 --> 00:23:06,199
- Dasar bajingan!
- Tutup mulutmu, Berengsek!

230
00:23:16,710 --> 00:23:18,045
Mati kau, Berengsek!

231
00:23:19,004 --> 00:23:20,005
Mati saja kau!

232
00:23:20,088 --> 00:23:20,964
Tunggu.

233
00:23:24,760 --> 00:23:26,178
Hari ini datang juga.

234
00:23:26,803 --> 00:23:28,221
Kau keren.

235
00:23:33,435 --> 00:23:34,603
Seperti kata Saeroyi,

236
00:23:35,270 --> 00:23:36,688
aku akan pergi dengan tenang.

237
00:23:43,570 --> 00:23:45,155
Bagaimana dengan mereka?

238
00:23:47,324 --> 00:23:48,325
Apa?

239
00:23:49,034 --> 00:23:50,744
Lihatlah keadaanku.

240
00:23:50,827 --> 00:23:53,330
Aku sendiri bahkan tak bisa bertahan.

241
00:23:54,539 --> 00:23:56,541
Biarkan mereka di sini dahulu...

242
00:23:56,625 --> 00:23:57,501
Hentikan.

243
00:24:00,879 --> 00:24:02,464
Tak usah bicara lagi.

244
00:24:07,427 --> 00:24:09,846
Kau mulai membuatku menyesal

245
00:24:11,515 --> 00:24:13,225
pernah bekerja untukmu.

246
00:24:17,270 --> 00:24:18,438
Bos sejati

247
00:24:19,690 --> 00:24:21,608
adalah orang
yang berani bertanggung jawab.

248
00:24:28,073 --> 00:24:28,991
Mati!

249
00:24:29,658 --> 00:24:30,826
Mati saja!

250
00:25:03,942 --> 00:25:06,403
Tunggu. Di sana. Berhenti di depan.

251
00:25:44,775 --> 00:25:47,486
Mati saja kau, dasar zombi.

252
00:25:53,200 --> 00:25:55,243
Aku tidak seperti dahulu.

253
00:25:59,289 --> 00:26:00,624
<i>Kau harus ingat ini.</i>

