782
01:13:23,058 --> 01:13:26,103
Katakan enak. Kita harus pilih dia.

783
01:13:31,316 --> 01:13:32,651
Apa sesuai dengan seleramu?

784
01:13:41,243 --> 01:13:42,202
Apa kau...

785
01:13:43,203 --> 01:13:44,496
